#

Hearty Vegetable Minestrone Soup

45 min
$12
250 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganLow-calorie

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasyHealthy

Description

A comforting and nourishing vegetable soup packed with fiber and vitamins.

Ingredients

  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • onion, diced: 1 medium
  • carrots, diced: 2 medium
  • celery stalks, diced: 2
  • garlic, minced: 2 cloves
  • zucchini, diced: 1 medium
  • green beans, chopped: 1 cup
  • canned diced tomatoes: 1 can (14 oz)
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • canned kidney beans, drained: 1 can (15 oz)
  • pasta (small shapes like ditalini): 1 cup
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • italian seasoning: 1 teaspoon
